{"tid":1591980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(主線)鶳首要目標理應定為一眾反對成立獨立調查委員會的建制狗官","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:19.000Z","uid":300745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"305b72c0995c039f45fd1dc3151b67d5cfdc8ac2","tid":1591980,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"第一，我們現在行動一直無法有效地懲罰他們出賣香港人，該是時候令他們負出代價<br />\n<br />\n第二， 目標若定為警犬，部份手足難以突破心理關口 ，故可定為高等玩家目標<br />\n<br />\n第三， 愛國者，廢佬等嘍囉 ， 可用於升級用，但不應定為首要目標<br />\n<br />\n第四，牠們極為怕死， 故可給予他們極大心理壓力， 就算佢地閉門不出，或重金請保鏢，都可收不戰而屈人之兵效果<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要，佢地有咩冬瓜豆腐意外，應該無咩人會割，但士氣一定會大增<br />\n<br />\n突破瓶頸<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"6105dfff924696641f79616679ae2380522b068a","tid":1591980,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"36acb746174fa288aa65048c9f0dc1ca07b34417","tid":1591980,"uid":267258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4f76ffbf28de9947f26291ea71558ecd72fa50e","tid":1591980,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"57c42365d02f3f490abdb1ec07724065698e0e53","tid":1591980,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"fa359876e7a61954f58c5b80442fe7ed413e9db8","tid":1591980,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d29a8ba66fad34edce478223b24ca3fe9cac0e00","tid":1591980,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid